# Example token file for the Llama 3.1 8B gated tokenizer.
# Copy to .env (or hf_token.env) and fill in your real value.
#
# IMPORTANT:
# - This file must NEVER be committed.
# - Run: chmod 600 .env   (or the name you choose)
# - The download_8b_tokenizer.sh script (and manual instructions) will read it.
#
# Get your approved token from https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Meta-Llama-3.1-8B
# (You must have Meta approval for the gated repo.)

HF_TOKEN=your_approved_hf_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx_token_here

# Optional: you can also use a YAML-style file if you prefer structured config
# (the helper primarily uses .env / KEY=val, but you can parse YAML yourself if needed).
